-- Bogdanka Won't Back New World Resources Takeover Bid Today, Parkiet Says
-- B y   M a c i e j   M a r t e w i c z
-- 2010-10-21T04:38:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/bogdanka-won-t-back-new-world-resources-takeover-bid-today-parkiet-says.html
The management of Lubelski Wegiel
Bogdanka SA, Poland’s only publicly traded coal producer,
won’t support a takeover bid by New World Resources NV of the
Czech Republic in a statement due today, Parkiet reported,
without saying where it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maciej Martewicz at 
 mmartewicz@bloomberg.net  